  "title": "Project Engineer (contract)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Conduct security equipment installation, testing, commissioning, and system programming</li><li>Participate in project management</li><li>Assist and provide technical support to sales and other departments</li><li>Carry out system troubleshooting and problem-solving</li><li>Conduct on-site client training</li><li>Develop in-depth system design and drawings using AutoCAD</li><li>Maintain a high level of knowledge in security systems</li><li>Any other ad-hoc duties as assigned by supervisor</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements</strong></p><ul><li>Working experience in security and/or electronic system project implementation and commissioning, preferably in a multinational environment</li><li>Basic IT knowledge in security hardware, networks, and databases</li><li>Familiarity with security access control, video surveillance, and alarm system products and systems is an advantage</li><li>Willing to work on-site</li><li>Project management experience is an advantage</li><li>Past experience with Lenel, Cisco, and S2 systems is an advantage</li></ul><p>Interested applicants, please email your resume to <em>Andre Chua Jing Ming</em></p><p>Email: andrechua@recruitexpress.com.sg</p><p>CEI Reg No: R1989053</p><p>EA Licence No: 99C4599</p><p>Recruit Express Pte Ltd</p>",
